import React from 'react' const WeatherCard = (tempInfo) => { const {name,temp,humidity,pressure,wearthermood,speed,country,sunset} =tempInfo; let sec = sunset; let date = new Date(sec * 1000); let timeStr = `${date.getHours()}` return ( <>
{temp}°
{wearthermood}
{name},{country}
{new Date().toLocaleString()}
{/* our four part */}

{sunset}PM

{humidity}
Humidity

{pressure}
Pressure

{speed}
Speed

) } export default WeatherCard
